prefs-vector-enable-vector-1-help: Yuma din be tooni kanna, ti nyɛla ban yɛn kpaŋsiri vector nahiŋgbana ŋɔ. Vector fali ŋɔ ni che ka a tooi nyari yɛlikura zaŋ kpa vector (as of December 2019). A yi bɔri ni a deei baŋsim zaŋ kpa bee ninneesim, nyin yoomi [[mw:Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements|project page]].
